                                                                                    experience.'},
                             {class:'logo-card-3', h2:'National Footprint.',   p :'Many of our clients operate throughout the country. We are one of the largest
                                                                                    and most geographically diverse consulting groups  which allows us to best service
                                                                                    their needs.'},
                             {class:'logo-card-4', h2:'Excellent Service.',    p :'Often times our clients do not have full control over  timing for their deals and the
                                                                                    Consulting  team has a knack for making miracles happen.'}] %}


    {% for item in advantageCards %}

    <div class="advantage-card">

      <div class={{item.class}}></div>

      <h2>{{item.h2}}</h2>

      <p>{{item.p}}</p>

    </div>

    {% endfor %}

  </div>

  <a href="#" class="button-contact">
    <span>Contact us now</span><div class="arrow"></div>
  </a>

